high_descs: Turn right and head towards the apple on the table to your right.
Pick up apple from the table.
Turn right, walk passed the chair on your left, turn left and walk towards the fridge on your left.
Open the fridge, place the apple on the top shelf inside the fridge, close the fridge for the apple to cool down, open the fridge and take out the apple.
Turn right and head towards the white bin to the right of the fridge.
Place the apple in the bin.
anns.task_desc: Place a cool apple in the white bin.

high_descs: Turn and face the apple on the counter.
Pick up the apple on the counter.
Turn left, then right to get to the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the apple inside, then close the door. Then, remove the apple.
Turn right then left to face the trash can.
Put the apple in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put an apple in the trash.

high_descs: turn around to face the kitchen island
pick the green apple up off of the kitchen island
turn and walk over to the refrigerator
open the refrigerator and place the green apple inside to cool, then take it back out
turn and walk to the white garbage bin
place the apple inside the garbage bin
anns.task_desc: place a cooled apple inside of the garbage bin
